ple suffered from ill health-related health in 2021/22.



</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-31_ pf-text-1">The Care Quality Commission (CQC) mandates that all health and social care providers must ensure their staff receive adequate training.






</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-33_ pf-text-1">Compliance with CSTF can lead to a reduction in workplace incidents and improve patient care outcomes.







