</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-44_ pf-text-1"><strong>Core Skills Training Framework (CSTF)</strong> - A framework developed to standardise statutory and mandatory training across health and social care sectors, ensuring consistency and quality of training.







