</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-52_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-53_ pf-text-1"><strong>Health and Social Care Act 2008 (Regulated Activities) Regulations 2014 </strong>- These regulations ensure that care providers meet essential quality and safety standards.




</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-55_ pf-text-1"><strong>The Health and Safety at Work Act 1974</strong> - Mandates employers ensure the health, safety, and welfare of their employees.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-57_ pf-text-1"><strong>Care Quality Commission (CQC) Regulations</strong> - CQC requires that care providers ensure their staff are adequately trained and competent.







</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-59_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-60_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-61_ pf-heading-1-h3">CSTF face to face mandatory training</h3><p class="sc-edLa-Dd hZPWCc pf-63_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">CSTF classroom Mandatory Training is a yearly refresher course for all healthcare professionals, whether part-time, full-time, or agency workers. This course is aligned to the UK Core Skills Training Framework (CSTF) and meets all major framework training requirements.































































